A/10, V/10, movie voted one of the best 100 movies ever made. Henry Fonda, Charles Bronson, Claudia Cardinale, Keenan Wynn.  CODYBOSS1969 thank you for an excellent quality movie, it is your masterpiece really when considering this movie is well over 2 hours long. Good on you mate. In the opening scene, look  for the interaction between Keenan Wynn and a nuisance fly, Wynn's facial expression, trying to blow a fly off his face, a classic, they don't make movies like this anymore.

To oldtimer48, Any movie buff who is worth half his salt knows the difference between Jack Elam and Keenan Winn. Keenan Winn is the auctioneer and sheriff of Flagstaff, and does not evan show up till after 1 hr and 45 minutes into the movie. One should be sure of his facts before posting.

To oldtimer48, Any movie buff who is worth half his salt knows the difference between Jack Elam and Keenan Wynn. Keenan Wynn is the auctioneer and sheriff of Flagstaff, and does not evan show up till after 1 hr and 45 minutes into the movie. One should be sure of his facts before posting.
Just to make a correction; the town's name was Flagstone and Keenan's last name is spelled with a 'y', not an 'i'. v - 10, a - 10
